  "text": "The method of analysing the energy consumption of the ARM Cortex-M4 processor is one proposed by Tiwari et al. [CITATION_1] . This method models the energy consumption of a processor on the ISA level, and can be used to estimate the energy consumption of a given sequence of assembly instructions. It does so by taking statistical energy measurements of the processor for each instruction, for every possible pair of instructions, and for external effects.",
